description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Race Start Warm-Up' from the channel Dani Hansen.
The workout falls under Warm-up/Warm-up.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Competitor vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement. The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Get ready to race with Dani as you build power and quickness by adjusting your slide during start sequences.

Max rhythm: 36, Format: Technique ...
